commits.author: Robert Muir
commits.sourceNew:
/** * Retrieve the ordinal for the current document (previously * set by {@link #setDocument(int)} at the specified index. *

* An index ranges from {@code 0} to {@code cardinality()-1}. * The first ordinal value is at index {@code 0}, the next at index {@code 1}, * and so on, as for array indexing. * @param index index of the ordinal for the document. * @return ordinal for the document at the specified index. */ public abstract long ordAt(int index);
